items.content_html:
Summary

Adds browser compatibility data for the origin and excludeOrigin properties of browsingData.RemovalOptions introduced into Chrome in release 74.

Related issues

Provides for the browser compatibility data requirements of mdn/content#27629. Related documentation changes in mdn/content#38902
